TreeLens
========

TreeLens generalizes the engineering core of a production Photoshop MCP server
(a server-side, diff-synced mirror of a host application's hierarchical state,
navigated by query tools) into a reusable, host-agnostic pattern for building
MCP servers over applications with large live hierarchies (Photoshop, Figma,
Unity, ...).

