Status
------
Published under MIT. The pattern's mirror core is proven in production
(Photoshop); this reference is an independent extraction of it, validated by the
conformance suite (not the production binary). Several mechanisms (mutation
batching, safe-wait / command serialization, diff localization) are still in
design — see docs/open-problems.md.
